Subject: drm/komeda: Adds register dump support for gcu, lup and dou
Git-commit: aefdaa15e54c092709cb926a4b2732986386ef34
Patch-mainline: v5.5-rc1
References: bsc#1152489

Adds to support register dump on lpu and dou of pipeline and gcu on D71

Changes since v1:
- For a constant format without additional arguments, use seq_puts()
instead of seq_printf().

